  <description>
	  <p>Instant, complete encyclopedic information about each chemical element is available.
	    An indispensable application for students studying chemical disciplines.</p>
	  <p>Features:</p>
	  <ul>
      <li>It has a simple and clear interface.</li>
      <li>A customizable online multilingual translation of the application interface.</li>
	  </ul>
	</description>

